data.description: Newly Listed East valley home features a modern architectural design that combines sleek lines and contemporary elements, adding a touch of sophistication to the overall aesthetic. The design allows for plenty of natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout the space.With beautiful views from various rooms and patios, this home offers an ever-changing backdrop of natural beauty.The kitchen and bathrooms have been recently revamped and updated, ensuring a modern and stylish look. The solid surface countertops not only add a touch of elegance but also provide durability and easy maintenance.One of the charming features of this home is the adorable breezeway entrance. This breezeway adds character and offers a cozy spot to relax or entertain guests.The large patios provide ample space for outdoor living and entertaining. Whether you want to host a barbecue, enjoy a morning coffee, or simply soak up the sun, the spacious patios offer a perfect setting to enjoy the outdoors.
